  npcName: The Guy
  soulAvt: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7c351e0f1f3909f45acee25a96aa0685, type: 3}
  lines:
  - '*&%^&* What the hell are you?! Let me go!'
  - This is Limbo, a place souls must pass through after their lifespan ends, awaiting
    karmic judgment.
  - ' Dead? What the f*** are you talking about?! What the hell is death?!'
  - ...
  - ' Impossible? Did I really die?!'
  - ...
  - "HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA\u2026"
  - 'That''s good, no more indebted to the sh*tty life. So where do I go now? '
  - Follow me.
  - 'Seriously bro, where is this? '
  - This is Limbo, a place souls must pass through after their lifespan ends, awaiting
    karmic judgment.
  - ' I heard ya yapping from the beginning. What I need is the details. More details,
    understand? '
  - This is Limbo, a place souls must pass through-
  - 'Damn it, are you a robot? Why do you keep repeating the same thing? It''s so
    boring here. When I was alive, I complained about everything, but now I realize
    it''s quite fun up there. '
  - Fun? Boring?
  - 'That''s right! Up there, when you''re bored, you can just find some "fun" things
    to do. For example, go find a beautiful woman to "talk to", many things that
    stimulate you and keep you excited all day. Even things like stealing cars, chasing
    dogs,... In general, things that a country bumpkin like you should experience
    to know what life is like. '
  - (Country bumpkin? What is life like?)
  - 'If we have the chance, I''ll take you to experience it. '
  - (If you can find fun in the human world, why is it still boring? Isn't that place
    not worth living in, too?)
